title: GMC Mewat Notification 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 84 Senior Resident Posts
description: Shaheed Hasan Khan Government Medical College (GMC Mewat) has announced the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 84 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MD/ MS, DNB can grab this chance and apply for the GMC Mewat Notification 2025 . Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested candidates can attend the walk-in at the address given below....
